snippet.title: Sewer's Plague : Into the nest - Gameplay
snippet.description:
Our adventurers are sinking even deeper into these stinking sewers ! 
Blast your way through these putrid catacombs and defeat many ugly creatures in this wacky scorer game. This game was made during LudumDare48

Link to the game : https://nicolasmcls.itch.io/sewers-plague-into-the-nest
